    "1. **Monthly Batch Scoring**: \n",
    "   - Run the churn model monthly on all donors\n",
    "   - Store `churn_risk_score` in the database alongside donor record\n",
    "   - Update the Admin Donors dashboard to display risk level (Low/Medium/High badge)\n",
    "\n",
    "2. **API Endpoint**:\n",
    "   - POST `/api/donors/{id}/churn-risk` → returns `{churn_risk_score, risk_level, recommended_action}`\n",
    "   - Used by staff to check a specific donor's risk before outreach\n",
    "\n",
    "3. **Dashboard Widget**:\n",
    "   - \"Donors at Risk This Month\" card showing count of High/Medium risk donors\n",
    "   - Drill-down table: List all at-risk donors sorted by risk score\n",
    "   - Quick action buttons: \"Send Re-engagement Email\", \"Schedule Call\", \"View History\"\n",
    "\n",
    "4. **Recommended Actions by Risk Level**:\n",
    "   - **High Risk (>0.66)**: Immediate personal outreach (call or personalized email with impact report)\n",
    "   - **Medium Risk (0.33–0.66)**: Automated re-engagement email campaign + impact update\n",
    "   - **Low Risk (<0.33)**: Standard stewardship (monthly newsletter, thank-you post)\n",
